Whoa, girl!　Want to go digging?
I have a lightweight pickaxe that even you can handle!
It'll break after 25 digs, but it's light enough that you can dig without worrying about your strength!
As an added bonus, there's a pickaxe buried in the wall, too.。
Dig until all the pickaxes are gone, and then you can go home.。
The ore that comes out of the walls is slightly different on each level.
If you want rare ores, try to find the stairs to the bottom.。
The most important thing we need to watch out for is the lava under our feet.。
Depending on the direction you're digging, you might not be able to see what's ahead, so watch out!
When your HP is gone, of course, it's game over.。
The light-weight pickaxes are 3,000G each, wanna play?
Only the pickaxe I give you is a little sturdier.。
